response.original_title: Sabrina Carpenter: Live Primavera Sound Barcelona
response.overview: Sabrina Carpenter at Live Primavera Sound Barcelona showcases the singer and actress at her best. With hits like "Skin" and "Nonsense," she delivers a high-energy pop show filled with choreography and a direct connection with the audience, creating an unforgettable experience.
